{"tid":688433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★財爺網誌：香港金融科技 具發展優勢","createTime":"2018-06-03T08:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T11:11:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d4721f638a6ec06ab62938517128a2c4482b8c4b","tid":688433,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"陳茂波稱，香港作為國際金融中心，擁有一流的通訊基建及科研力量，有很大的優勢推動金融科技發展。現時<span style=\"color: red;\">數碼港已聚集了約250間金融科技企業，形成蓬勃的企業生態環境。過去4年，香港的金融科技企業合共獲得的投融資超過9億美元，比新加坡多近兩倍。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180603/bkn-20180603123627359-0603_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180603%2Fbkn-20180603123627359-0603_00842_001.html&d=EKBlxs2ezAfNZLerYJAvGwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9b412537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180603/bkn-20180603123627359-0603_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"abe94692d27450d2fc0aa78b2b0d7dc424cc8781","tid":688433,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8241d9126b76cdf1482566176e9a4babec61d12","tid":688433,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:22:19.000Z","msg":"HKNoIT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a16e48eb1de76a2a6cf96bbb510400ec740ed8","tid":688433,"uid":62011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:22:57.000Z","msg":"係咪即係用wechat呃支國人買金融產品？"},{"pid":"700be37870a34fdb0bb94375f709789f101c8c70","tid":688433,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8241d9126b76cdf1482566176e9a4babec61d12","tid":688433,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime